setEditBeginSelected

public void setEditBeginSelected(boolean selected)
Sets the CheckBox to selected and indicates that it's the initial value before editing. Thus, we are not asked to cancel edit if we didn't change the value.

Parameters:
selected - true if the checkbox is to be selected.
